Place compiled Rust binaries here:

  libs/Linux/libhyperframe_core.so
  libs/Mac/libhyperframe_core-arm64.dylib
  libs/Mac/libhyperframe_core-x86_64.dylib
  libs/Win/hyperframe_core.dll

Build instructions:
  cd hyperframe-core/
  cargo build --release
  cp target/release/libhyperframe_core.so ../hyperframe_sdk/hyperframe/libs/Linux/
